&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and stakeholder management abilities across global teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High attention to detail and organizational skills; able to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive, self-driven, and comfortable working independently or in virtual teams&lt;/li&gt;
