&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a commercially minded &lt;strong&gt;Legal Counsel&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing legal team and support the company’s global sales organisation. This is a collaborative role working closely with Sales and other business stakeholders to provide clear, pragmatic legal advice, support customer negotiations and help ensure that legal, regulatory, privacy and commercial risks are appropriately identified, communicated and managed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will act as a trusted legal partner to the business, helping stakeholders navigate customer and channel transactions with sound judgement and a practical, solutions-oriented approach. They will be confident in assessing risk, escalating issues where appropriate and working with more senior members of the legal team on complex or strategic matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for an adaptable lawyer who enjoys commercial contracting, thrives in a fast-paced software environment and wants to develop broader in-house experience while helping the business achieve its objectives in a legally robust and practical way.&lt;/p&gt;
