&lt;li&gt;Provide pragmatic, commercially focused legal advice to Sales and business stakeholders, supporting negotiations while ensuring material legal, regulatory, privacy and commercial risks are appropriately identified, assessed and managed, and advising on compliance, data protection and internal approval requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of practical solutions to contractual and commercial issues, balancing business objectives with appropriate risk mitigation and escalation where required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify potential contractual, legal or operational issues during negotiations and work proactively with internal stakeholders to resolve them efficiently and reduce the risk of disputes or delays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with the development and continuous improvement of contract templates, negotiation playbooks and legal processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the creation and delivery of training and awareness materials to help business stakeholders understand legal risks, contracting principles and company approval processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with colleagues across the Legal department and contribute to a positive, supportive and high-performing team culture.&lt;/li&gt;
